{"comments":"QR Code Format and Version Information — BCH encoding and placement.\n\n## Format Information\n\nFormat info encodes EC level (2 bits) and mask pattern (3 bits):\n- 5 data bits + 10 BCH error correction bits = 15 bits total\n- XOR'd with mask 101010000010010 (0x5412)\n- Placed near all three finder patterns\n\n## Version Information (Version 7+)\n\nVersion info encodes the QR version number:\n- 6 data bits + 12 BCH error correction bits = 18 bits total\n- Placed in two 3×6 blocks near top-right and bottom-left finders\n\n## BCH Encoding\n\nUses BCH (Bose-Chaudhuri-Hocquenghem) codes for error correction:\n- Format: BCH(15,5) with generator x^10 + x^8 + x^5 + x^4 + x^2 + x + 1\n- Version: BCH(18,6) with generator 1111100100101\n","declarations":[{"children":[],"comments":"Encode format information (EC level + mask pattern).\n\nFormat info is 5 bits (2 EC + 3 mask) with 10 BCH error correction bits,\nthen XOR'd with mask 101010000010010.\n","info":{"declType":"value","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Element","Component","QRCode","Types","ErrorCorrection"],"ErrorCorrection"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Element","Component","QRCode","Matrix","Mask"],"MaskPattern"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Int"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[72,58],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Element/Compound/QRCode/Matrix/FormatVersion.purs","start":[72,1]},"title":"encodeFormatInfo"},{"children":[],"comments":"Place format information in the matrix.\n","info":{"declType":"value","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[